formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. The estimated costs mentioned in Column A is as provided by the management. The estimates should not be construed as certification of forecasts or estimates.
2. The details mentioned in Annexure A such as carpet area, booking status, unit consideration, date of agreement to sale, encumbrance status, name, KYC and mobile numbers of allottees are as provided by the management. Received amount has been verified with the books of accounts. 
3. Land Cost includes amount incurred and paid to land owner under notarised joint development agreement. Subsequently, a lease deed was executed by landowners in favour of the promoter for which land cost has not been incurred. 
4. Where Sale Deed has been executed, date of sale deed has been considered in 'Date of Agreement of Sale' in Annexure.
5. As provided by the management, as per the settlement of case in High Court, 4 units - 504, 506, 507 and 508 have been allotted to Kalavant Binaben K. The "received amount" in Annexure has been taken as 1 due to system limitations.
6. KYC provided have been modified by adding 0 in the KYC numbers to make it compliant to system requirement of Annexure.
